{"word":"H4603 - מָעַל - mâʻal - maw-al' - Transgress","slug":"H4603","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מָעַל</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>mâʻal"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>maw-al'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Transgress"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05E2;&#x05DC; - ma&#x0302;&#x201B;al</b> - <i>maw-al'</i><p/>A primitive root; properly to <i>cover</i> up; used only figuratively to <i>act covertly</i>, that is, <i>treacherously: - </i>transgress, (commit, do a) tresspass (-ing)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4598\">H4598</a>, <a href=\"#/H4604\">H4604</a>"}]}